This paper is likely to belong to the Computer Vision (cs.CV) and Robotics (cs.RO) sub-categories as it deals with object detection in autonomous driving scenarios. The paper also explicitly models uncertainties, which suggests that it may belong to the Machine Learning (cs.LG) and Artificial Intelligence (cs.AI) sub-categories. Finally, the paper may also belong to the Natural Language Processing (cs.CL) sub-category as it mentions the difficulties of a human expert to label objects, which could be related to natural language processing tasks such as text classification.
